  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MultiDex
    Monkey patches the application context class loader in order to load classes from more than one dex file.
    MultiDex.V14
    Installer for platform versions 14, 15, 16, 17 and 18.
    MultiDex.V19
    Installer for platform versions 19.
    MultiDex.V4
    Installer for platform versions 4 to 13.
    MultiDexApplication
    Minimal MultiDex capable application.
    MultiDexExtractor
    Exposes application secondary dex files as files in the application data directory.
